⍝ RavelAxis.tc
⍝ ════════════

      ⎕IO←1

      ⍝ Precond: X simple scalar fraction or integer; implicit ⎕IO
      ⍝ inv: ⍴⍴Z ←→ 1+⍴⍴B  (rank increases by 1 with fractional X)
      B ← ⎕RVAL 2 (3 4) (,0 1 0 0 0)
      Z ← ,[0.5]B                             ⍝ laminate along new first axis
      (⍴⍴Z) ≡ 1+⍴⍴B
1
      ⍝ inv: ,B ←→ ,[⍳⍴⍴B]B   (ravel all axes = ravel)
      (,B) ≡ ,[⍳⍴⍴B]B
1
      ⍝ inv: ,[⍳0]B ←→ ,[1.1]B  (ravel no axes = add new last axis)
      (,[⍳0]B) ≡ ,[1.5]B
1
